---
import SiteLayout from "../layouts/SiteLayout.astro";
---

<SiteLayout
  title="About Us | Bella Rosa Italian Kitchen"
  description="About Bella Rosa Italian Kitchen in Charlotte."
>
  <main class="content-band page-frame">
    <div class="section-heading">
      <p class="eyebrow">About Us</p>
      <h1>About Bella Rosa</h1>
    </div>

    <section class="content-band">
      <div class="two-column-copy">
        <p>
          Bella Rosa serves Italian food made for weeknight dinners, family visits, and slower evenings over a bottle of wine.
          The menu keeps a few classics in place and changes with the season.
        </p>
        <p>
          We keep the room comfortable and the service straightforward. Come in for a table, order pickup, or ask us about
          hosting a small group.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="content-band">
      <h2>Kitchen notes</h2>
      <ul class="plain-list">
        <li>Slow-fermented dough and hand-built pasta where possible</li>
        <li>Simple sauces with fresh aromatics and fresh cheeses</li>
        <li>Vegetarian and gluten-free options marked on the menu</li>
        <li>Seasonal updates with current pricing online</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="content-band">
      <h2>FAQ</h2>
      <details>
        <summary>Do you seat walk-ins?</summary>
        <p>Yes, when availability allows. Reservations are recommended for weekend evenings.</p>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>Is there a gluten-free choice for pasta?</summary>
        <p>Yes. We can prepare gluten-free alternatives and can discuss shared kitchen handling protocols.</p>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>Do you host private events?</summary>
        <p>Absolutely. Please use our Catering inquiry form and we’ll plan timing and food style with you.</p>
      </details>
    </section>
  </main>
</SiteLayout>
